</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-44_ pf-text-1"><strong>Best practice</strong> - Adhering to guidelines endorsed by professional bodies like the Royal College of Nursing (RCN) and the General Medical Council (GMC) ensures that employment contracts reflect industry standards and promote a positive working environment conducive to patient care.


